{"tid":34671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當撈侵：為什麼我們要死守一個中國政策","createTime":"2016-12-11T15:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T18:40:50.000Z","uid":2087,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"199ad4d81c2c474ef94ba65aaa0e2d119494b3ac","tid":34671,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"美國總統當選人當撈侵接受福斯電視台訪問時質疑，如果支那有讓利，為何美國一定要遵守「一個中國」政策。<br />\n在這段昨天錄影，今日播出的訪談錄影中，當撈侵說他不想讓支那命令他要不要接台灣的電話。他還質疑若支那沒有在貿易等問題上讓步，美國為何要一直遵守「一個中國」政策。<br />\n當撈侵說：「除非我們和支那能在其他事情，像是貿易上達成協議，我不知道為什麼必須要受到一個中國政策約束（be bound by a one China policy）。」<br />\n除了貿易，當撈侵也說支那在匯率、北韓或者南海問題上不跟美國合作。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161211/1009972/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161211%2F1009972%2F&d=rR2gLQwBRv6q9Yu%2B0eW34JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=fd0bf3df\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161211/1009972/</a>"},{"pid":"c0bbceb1c0255cc5deac89e4b0bab7381955c01b","tid":34671,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"等侵本人入嚟解畫"},{"pid":"3568069a3399b544bd2ab11b543e7f4fea6e275e","tid":34671,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"China"},{"pid":"644e09a0592e7c20ff435f4a4f956185ed0a9329","tid":34671,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24b8bedb9fba342944c686e44a74679034ed81f5","tid":34671,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>China</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ab0a2dfbf66cd90809dcbdcbd6502e1d6f71ff","tid":34671,"u